 $Id$ 

 VGM Example E02
 Converting geometry from Root to Geant4
 ---------------------------------------
 
 Source: Root geometry file N03Example.root
         Geant4 novice N03 example
         
 1. Define environment variables 
    (see doc/INSTALL)
    
 2. Install Geant4 N03 example in E02 directory:
    cp -r ${G4INSTALL}/examples/novice/N03 .
    source env_setup.csh
    
 3. Update example for provided files:
    cp N03Example.root N03
    cp GNUmakefile N03
    cp ExN03DetectorConstruction.hh N03/include
    cp ExN03DetectorConstruction.cc N03/src
    cp ExN03PrimaryGeneratorAction.cc N03/src
    cp ExN03SteppingAction.cc N03/src
    rm N03/include/ExN03DetectorMessenger.hh
    rm N03/src/ExN03DetectorMessenger.cc
    
 4. Recompile 
    cd N03
    gmake
    
 5. Run example, the geometry will be imported during initialization
    exampleN03
